{
  "stem": "2004.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I-- as far as I can remember, they were even-- the Germans did permit to have classes for Jews in a Jewish school providing they were strictly for Jews.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were no other people in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know if was official or otherwise, but it was not done in a home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was done in a class.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was in one of the school classes in Gorlice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Krakow, it was in a home class.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Gorlice, it was in a Jewish type of-- it must have been part of a Jewish synagogue which was dedicated to be a Jewish school for the children.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were getting sort of an education in basic elementary education.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By the way, my education before the war, I finished six grades of elementary school, public school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, I was about to enter what we called gymnasium at the time, which is the equivalent of American high school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the war broke out, and I could not attend for the reason I stated before.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in Gorlice, it was type of-- it was difficult, especially for refugees.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were refugees.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We really were not people that lived in Gorlice, so obviously, we did not have a business.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What we had to live on is-- we managed to bring some of our belongings.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had some jewelry that we were able to sell to support ourselves and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was no income per se, except that we had to sell off some of our belongings which we were able to save when we left our hometown in Cieszyn.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we managed, sort of.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it wasn't-- it wasn't anything-- it wasn't a life of luxury, by any means.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
